{"tid":1000091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"任天堂支援Taiwanese  強國人崩潰","createTime":"2019-01-29T07:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T08:13:06.000Z","uid":184679,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"630f04ea3ee023eae581183acadfea4eefdc0d5c","tid":1000091,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:50:48.000Z","msg":"日本家庭遊戲機大廠任天堂（Nintendo）日前正式公佈Switch主機支援中文的更新事宜，卻因為官方英文公告中將繁體中文寫為「Taiwanese」，而非一般常用的「Chinese Traditional 」，意外引發中國網友在論壇發文指摘任天堂搞「台獨」，而台灣網友也忍不住推文：「玻璃（心）要碎啦」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，Switch在進行更新後，主機語言下載更新程式，可顯示簡體中文（Chinese Simplified）、韓文、繁體中文（Chinese Traditional）。但在任天堂於英文公告中，指更新後新增多種語言支援功能，包括Chinese、Korean以及Taiwanese。由於任天堂將繁體中文寫為「Taiwanese」，而非一般常用的「Chinese Traditional」，有中國網友發現後即指，「老任算是支持台「毒」？」<br />\n<br />\n台灣玩家則對任天堂的安排表示肯定，認為此舉代表注重台灣市場，以任天堂的嚴謹風格來說，推出中文介面已算是一大突破，甚至還有人直言：「看到Taiwanese就是爽」。至於中國網友在論壇貼出任天堂公告使用「Taiwanese」而發動抵制行動，台灣玩家則反斥：「中國可以玩任天堂嗎」、「中國要抵制好多東西」、「不是在反日？幹嘛玩任天堂」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190129/59197865\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197865&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMLY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=3f9c8118\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197865&h=673b5d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190129/59197865</a>"},{"pid":"9e644ecc6653e580973f90f137795fe002580ca6","tid":1000091,"uid":127120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"21c22646fe829304fb58b73d46db867e0a1734b8","tid":1000091,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T07:53:00.000Z","msg":"香港wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e3c434d14be5df85c95bdd475702b658d6